# *Numpy Average*

- The code below calculates the average ofÂ `example_array`Â and saves the value toÂ `example_average`. The resulting average of this array isÂ `20`.

```python
example_array = np.array([24, 16, 30, 10, 12, 28, 38, 2, 4, 36])
example_average = np.average(example_array)
print(example_average)
```

